Frequently Asked Questions

How does the AI interviewer work?

Our AI interviewer uses advanced natural language processing to understand your responses and provide realistic follow-up questions, simulating a real interview experience.

Can I access my previous interview sessions?

Yes, all your previous sessions are saved in your account. You can review them anytime to track your progress and identify areas for improvement.

Is my data kept confidential?

Absolutely. We take data privacy very seriously. All your information and interview sessions are encrypted and stored securely. We never share your data with third parties.
